main event: Multiple witnesses reported observing 3 or 4 unidentified objects in the sky on 15 July 1965.
interesting points: The objects were seen at a distance of 10-15 miles and were visible for several minutes., No lights or discernible characteristics were observed on the objects., The objects appeared to be dark in color and moved approximately straight., The sighting occurred during clear weather with unlimited visibility., 12 employees of O'Hare Airport also reported seeing a round object about the size of a dime reflecting light.
sighted object: 3 or 4 unidentified objects in the sky
